OL,3,CRobbie Williams to feature on Port
OL,4,CVale shirt
OL,6,FPort Vale Football Club have announced
OL,7,Fa two-year partnership with superstar
OL,8,Fsinger and life-long supporter, Robbie
OL,9,FWilliams.
OL,11,FHis initials 'RW' will feature on the
OL,12,F2026/27, and 2027/28 home and away
OL,13,Fkits, and he will be working to
OL,14,Fhighlight the club's charitable work
OL,15,Fas an ambassador for the Port Vale
OL,16,FFoundation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
