FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781394470
OL,3,CRobbie Williams to feature on Port
OL,4,CVale shirt
OL,6,F"I'm back here and back involved
OL,7,Fbecause of (Chair and Co-Owner) Carol
OL,8,F(Shanahan) and the family, and what
OL,9,Fthey have created backstage. Being
OL,10,Fembraced again by the Port Vale family
OL,11,Fhas been very important to me, and it
OL,12,Ffeels wonderful."
OL,14,FRobbie Williams was born and raised
OL,15,Fjust a short distance from the club's
OL,16,Fhome at Vale Park, and returned to
OL,17,FBurslem in 2022 for a special
OL,18,Fhomecoming concert at the stadium.
OL,20,F"A global superstar"
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@QO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
