PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781394470
OL,3,CRobbie Williams to feature on Port
OL,4,CVale shirt
OL,6,FPort Vale Chief Executive Officer,
OL,7,FMatt Hancock said:
OL,9,F"This partnership means a huge amount
OL,10,Fto us here at the football club, and
OL,11,Fwe are absolutely delighted to be
OL,12,Fworking alongside Robbie.
OL,14,F"He is not only a global superstar,
OL,15,Fbut also a genuine supporter of the
OL,16,Fclub with a deep and personal
OL,17,Fconnection to our town. It's that
OL,18,Fauthenticity which makes this so
OL,19,Fpowerful.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
