OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,345,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1781394470
OL,3,CRobbie Williams to feature on Port
OL,4,CVale shirt
OL,6,F"From the very first conversations, it
OL,7,Fwas clear this was about Robbie's life-
OL,8,Flong love for Port Vale and making a
OL,9,Ftangible difference to people's lives.
OL,11,F"The support and exposure the
OL,12,Fpartnership will give to the club and
OL,13,FFoundation will help us reach more
OL,14,Fpeople, create more opportunities and
OL,15,Fcontinue using the club as a force for
OL,16,Fgood."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
